That, for example, is why few folks are willing to criticize their colleagu=
es or former companies: today=E2=80=99s former co-worker or former manager =
is tomorrow=E2=80=99s angel investor or job reference, and memories are lon=
g and reputations longer. That holds particularly true for venture capitali=
